":"Frank Probst: pic#123371686","article":"I've been on Subterranean Press's e-mail list for months, and I don't remember even seeing this, so it must have sold out quite a while ago.  <br /><br />I'm planning on getting my regular store-bought copy signed by as many of the authors as I can track down.  I'm hoping to get you and Gardner and as many others as I can at Sasquan.  Neil Gaiman has limited his number of signing events, so he'll be tough.  Gillian Flynn is about to become even more famous for \"Gone Girl\", which I guess means she'll be doing a lot more or a lot fewer signings.  Lisa Tuttle (who I was very happy to see included) will be a Guest of Honor at the World Horror Convention in Atlanta in May, and I'm assuming she'll do at least one signing.<br /><br />Anyone know about any of the other writers?","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"September 6 2014, 20:52:22 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Must have sold out a while ago...","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=2246029","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Frank Probst","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2587046","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=70873652&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Frank Probst","ctime_ts":1410036742,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/123213346/13990271","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/382851.html?thread=19510659#t19510659","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/382851.html?thread=19510659#t19510659","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/382851.html?thread=19510659#t19510659","name":"expand","title